diffusive mass transport, which we argue is the consequence of\na form of effective self-propulsion resulting from the polar coupling between\nmotors and filaments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Sep 2010 11:42:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 19 Nov 2010 17:25:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-22"}
